00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:07,760
it's something like sensation or perception, not just sort of what we mean by intuition

162
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,560
where I can't really explain it but I have this feeling.

163
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,560
It's not feeling.

164
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:14,320
It's really a matter of sensation or sensibility.

