00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:21,600
could know anything of them a priori.

167
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:26,920
If on the other hand, the object conforms to the nature of our faculty of intuition,

168
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:33,640
that is to say our faculties of sensation and of understanding, I can then easily conceive

169
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:37,200
the possibility of such an a priori knowledge.

170
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:42,280
So if it's my job to match the world, I have no reason to think that my mind is built in

171
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:46,200
such a way that I could have a priori knowledge of the way that world is.

172
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,760
That world is independent of my mind.

173
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:48,760
It's far into my mind.

