00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:54,440
I have no reason to believe that my mind matches it and certainly no guarantee that it will.

175
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:58,760
So it looks as if I can't know anything about an a priori independently of experience of

176
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:05,440
it, but if the world is something that has to conform to me, or let's be more precise

