00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:03,560
Now I mentioned that I think Kant is in a sense doing the reverse.

190
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,600
Why?

191
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:10,680
Because realism would say our concepts have to revolve around an external world, a world

