00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:36,880
That is really taking us back to a picture where we're at the center of the world.

198
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:39,920
We're at the center in the sense that our minds are constructing the objects in the

199
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:40,920
world.

